{"prompt": "Generate a website for a freelance design agency. The website should be artistic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Artisan Design Studio</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #e0f2f7; /* Light blue background */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, #0077b6, #90e0ef); /* Primary blue gradient */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            margin: 5px 0 0;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        section h2 {\n            color: #0077b6; /* Primary blue */\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid #0077b6; /* Primary blue accent */\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #0077b6; /* Primary blue */\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #0077b6; /* Primary blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        a {\n            color: #0077b6; /* Primary blue */\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            display: inline-block;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #0077b6; /* Primary blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #023e8a; /* Darker blue */\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Artisan Design Studio</h1>\n            <p>Crafting Visual Narratives for Your Brand</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>We are a passionate freelance design collective specializing in creating unique and impactful visual solutions. From branding and web design to illustration and UI/UX, we bring your ideas to life with a touch of artistry.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Branding & Identity</h3>\n                    <p>Develop a strong brand presence with custom logos, color palettes, and style guides.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Web Design & Development</h3>\n                    <p>Create engaging and user-friendly websites that capture your brand's essence.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Graphic Design</h3>\n                    <p>From marketing materials to social media graphics, we design for maximum impact.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>UI/UX Design</h3>\n                    <p>Enhance user experience with intuitive and aesthetically pleasing interface designs.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Artisan Design Studio. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}